query:
SELECT ff.*, ef.id as execucao_id, ef.formandoId, f.nome as formando_nome, tc.nome as cenario_nome
FROM fotos_formando ff
JOIN execucao_formando ef ON ff.execucaoFormandoId = ef.id
JOIN formandos f ON ef.formandoId = f.id
LEFT JOIN tipos_cenario tc ON ff.cenarioId = tc.id
ORDER BY ff.id DESC
LIMIT 10
